raw_data.title: Level 1 - System Installer
raw_data.description: This installer is responsible for basic security systems installation (running wire, making connections). This position requires a minimum of 1 year of related experience or security systems installation technical training.
raw_data.education_and_experience_substitution: OSHA 10-hour safety training, Passed background check for a security systems installer, fluent reading and speaking the English language; physically able to climb ladders and lift up to 40 pounds, drivers license

labor_categories.years_experience: OSHA 10-hour safety training, Passed background check for a security systems installer, fluent reading and speaking the English language; physically able to climb ladders and lift up to 40 pounds, drivers license

raw_data.title: Level 2 - Security Technician
raw_data.description: This state licensed security systems technician is responsible for general security system installation and service. Qualifications include training on access control or video systems and at least one factory certification. A minimum of 3 years experience is required.
raw_data.education_and_experience_substitution: All Level 1 requirements plus: State Licensed Class D Low Voltage Electrician, training on access control or video system installation with at least one factory certification. Three (3) Years experience.
raw_data.required_certifications_or_licenses: State Licensed Class D Low Voltage Electrician, one factory certification, License State of Massachusetts

labor_categories.years_experience: All Level 1 requirements plus: State Licensed Class D Low Voltage Electrician, training on access control or video system installation with at least one factory certification. Three (3) Years experience.

raw_data.title: Level 3 - Senior Security Technician
raw_data.description: This state licensed security systems technician is responsible for advanced security system installation of service. Qualifications include multiple factory training certifications. A minimum of 5 years experience is required.
raw_data.education_and_experience_substitution: All Level 2 requirements plus: Multiple factory certifications in both access control and video systems.  Five (5) years experience.
raw_data.required_certifications_or_licenses: Multiple factory certifications in both access control and video systems, License State of Massachusetts

labor_categories.years_experience: All Level 2 requirements plus: Multiple factory certifications in both access control and video systems.  Five (5) years experience.
